WEBVTT

00:00:02.920 --> 00:00:05.350
<i>Kizaki-san has beautiful eyelashes.</i>

00:00:09.980 --> 00:00:11.720
<i>And she can play musical instruments.</i>

00:00:19.150 --> 00:00:21.460
That was so good, Kizaki-san.

00:00:21.460 --> 00:00:23.960
I've been playing it my 
whole life. It better be.

00:00:23.960 --> 00:00:24.750
<i>She's so cool...</i>

00:00:25.230 --> 00:00:27.010
<i>And she's my friend!</i>

00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:30.430
Hey, Akebi-san...

00:00:31.250 --> 00:00:35.000
You've been looking at me a lot lately.

